        "timestamp": "2018-04-12 22:21:10.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> So who is responsible for that test?  Let's get rid of it, unless\n > there is some logical reason for it's existence.\n\n@DeWayne Git blame and 'git show 5a5d6aeda' point to a Sindhu A <arcot.sindhuri@huawei.com> for SDNCNotifyResource Test\nand for SDNCAdapterRestImpl Test the same person committed it 'git show 800ecc737'.\n\nI've added him to this patch. Sindhu, why do you think the tests are failing given the new dependency?",
